    <item>
      <title>习近平新一轮军事清洗是他驱逐敌对势力以来最大规模的清洗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/xi-s-biggest-military-purge-in-years-spotlights-frustration-with-armed-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席首次罢免数名高级将领，旨在铲除共产党内部的敌对势力。如今，他甚至还罢免了自己忠诚的一名将领，这表明军队出现了新的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/xi-s-biggest-military-purge-in-years-spotlights-frustration-with-armed-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命前参议员戴维·珀杜 (David Perdue) 为驻华大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-perdue-as-us-ambassador-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他提名前参议员戴维·珀杜 (David Perdue) 担任美国驻华大使，让这位商界高管出身的政治家担任他最重要的外交职位之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-perdue-as-us-ambassador-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:15:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本考虑与特朗普进行谈判，包括削减汽车关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/japan-eyes-talks-with-trump-that-include-cutting-auto-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本外务大臣岩屋毅称，东京方面有意与当选总统唐纳德·特朗普展开贸易谈判，但双方达成共识，将取消汽车及汽车零部件的关税列入谈判议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/japan-eyes-talks-with-trump-that-include-cutting-auto-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 01:50:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
