    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命戴维·萨克斯为白宫人工智能和加密货币主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-sacks-as-white-house-ai-and-crypto-czar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他正在选择 Craft Ventures LLC 的风险投资家戴维·萨克斯担任他的人工智能和加密沙皇，这个新设立的职位凸显了这位当选总统推动两个快速发展行业的意图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-sacks-as-white-house-ai-and-crypto-czar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国领导人的关键盟友现在希望他下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-korea-ruling-party-chief-seeks-yoon-s-suspension-in-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国执政党领导人表示，应尽快暂停总统尹锡烈的职务，这一立场的突然转变将使弹劾议案更有可能获得通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-korea-ruling-party-chief-seeks-yoon-s-suspension-in-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯与特朗普国家安全助理会见乌克兰高级官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/vance-trump-national-security-aides-meet-top-ukraine-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰一名高级官员周四会见了美国当选副总统 JD 万斯以及当选总统唐纳德特朗普的国家安全团队成员，乌克兰正准备迎接即将进入第四个年头的美国对俄战争政策的重大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/vance-trump-national-security-aides-meet-top-ukraine-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:11:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本基本工资创纪录上涨，为日本央行加息留有余地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/japan-base-pay-gains-by-record-keeping-door-open-for-boj-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本普通工人的基本工资上涨了创纪录的水平，这进一步表明经济正在向良性循环迈进，这将支持市场对央行近期加息的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/japan-base-pay-gains-by-record-keeping-door-open-for-boj-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 23:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员恩斯特拒绝支持赫格塞斯，让陷入困境的候选人陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-senator-ernst-declines-to-back-hegseth-leaving-embattled-nominee-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党人乔尼·恩斯特 (Joni Ernst) 是一名战斗老兵和强奸幸存者，在军事问题上对共和党同事有影响力，他明确拒绝支持皮特·赫格塞斯 (Pete Hegseth) 陷入困境的国防部长提名，并呼吁对针对他的指控进行进一步调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gop-senator-ernst-declines-to-back-hegseth-leaving-embattled-nominee-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
